    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/optimizing_server_utilization_5D37BA9E.html&quot; guid=&quot;_xDOpYOaREd6w5Z3dNqpXmw&quot;>Optimizing Server Utilization&lt;/a> - Optimize server workloads to maximize the value&#xD;
